name: Colors from the World by Francesco Fanti

metadata.name: Peaceful Sea
metadata.description:
There are times in life when you feel like you don't have a purpose and that's not necessarily bad!

The best thing to do on these occasions is to immerse yourself in nature, free your mind and enjoy the wonders of the earth like a quiet and peaceful sunset over the sea. This will invigorate you and refuel you with new energy ready to live another day in the best possible way.
